<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Aurelius | AI Accountability Partner Built on Stoic Philosophy</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Journal daily. Get scored nightly. Face the truth weekly. Aurelius is your AI accountability partner — Stoic judgment, daily scoring, and weekly narratives that tell you what you won't tell yourself.">
  <meta property="og:title" content="Aurelius — Your AI Accountability Partner">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Journal daily. Get scored nightly. Face the truth weekly. A discipline system built on Stoic philosophy.">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:image" content="aurelius-bust.png">
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="Aurelius — Your AI Accountability Partner">
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Journal daily. Get scored nightly. Face the truth weekly.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;500&family=Geist:wght@400;500;600&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    :root {
      --bg: #0e1016;
      --text: #f0f0f0;
      --text-muted: #888;
      --accent-teal: #5eb8c7;
      --accent-gold: #d4a500;
      --accent-gold-hover: #c49800;
      --error: #f59e0b;
      --card-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      --card-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      --card-border-hover: rgba(94, 184, 199, 0.4);
      --font: 'Geist', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    }

    html {
      font-size: 16px;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      font-family: var(--font);
      background-color: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    }

    .sr-only {
      position: absolute;
      width: 1px;
      height: 1px;
      padding: 0;
      margin: -1px;
      overflow: hidden;
      clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);
      white-space: nowrap;
      border: 0;
    }

    /* ── Nav ── */
    nav {
      padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      z-index: 10;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      background: rgba(14, 16, 22, 0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }

    .logo {
      display: block;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .logo-img {
      height: 80px;
      width: auto;
      display: block;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .nav-link {
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .nav-link:hover {
      color: var(--accent-teal);
    }

    .nav-btn {
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      transition: background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
      background: var(--accent-teal);
      color: var(--bg);
      border: none;
    }

    .nav-btn:hover {
      background: #4da3b2;
    }

    /* ── Sections ── */
    .section {
      padding: 6rem 2rem;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .section-heading {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 2.25rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .section-subtitle {
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 2rem;
      padding: 10rem 3rem 3rem;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    .hero::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      right: -5%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      width: 45%;
      height: 65%;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.06) 0%, rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.02) 35%, transparent 65%);
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .hero-left {
      flex: 1.15;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      max-width: 420px;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .hero-identity {
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero-action {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .hero-action .btn-gold {
      margin-top: 0.75rem;
    }

    .hero-right {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      background: transparent;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .wordmark {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.35em;
      color: var(--accent-teal);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .hero-headline {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.4;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      text-align: left;
    }

    .hero-subheadline {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
      text-align: left;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .hero-image-wrapper {
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .hero-image-wrapper::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      width: 70%;
      height: 70%;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.18) 0%, rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.08) 30%, rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.02) 55%, transparent 70%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      z-index: -1;
      filter: blur(40px);
    }

    .hero-image {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 520px;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.12)) drop-shadow(0 0 50px rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.05));
    }

    .hero-hook-setup {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .hero-hook-punch {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--accent-teal);
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    /* ── Buttons ── */
    .btn-gold {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.875rem 2.5rem;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-family: var(--font);
      font-weight: 600;
      background: var(--accent-teal);
      color: var(--bg);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .btn-gold:hover {
      background: #4da3b2;
    }

    .btn-outline {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.875rem 2.5rem;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-family: var(--font);
      font-weight: 500;
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--accent-teal);
      border: 1px solid var(--accent-teal);
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .btn-outline:hover {
      background: var(--accent-teal);
      color: var(--bg);
    }

    /* ── Problem ── */
    .problem {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .problem h2 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 2.25rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .pain-points {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .pain-points li {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .problem-closer {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      color: var(--accent-teal);
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    /* ── Solution ── */
    .solution {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .solution h2 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 2.25rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .solution p {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    }

    /* ── Timeline ── */
    .timeline-section {
      padding: 3.5rem 2rem;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .timeline {
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 3rem;
    }

    .timeline::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 7px;
      top: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 2px;
      background: var(--accent-teal);
      opacity: 0.4;
    }

    .timeline-step {
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .timeline-step:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .timeline-step::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: -2.85rem;
      top: 0.5rem;
      width: 14px;
      height: 14px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent-teal);
      border: 2px solid var(--bg);
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .timeline-time {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--accent-gold);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .timeline-label {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }

    .timeline-desc {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* ── Features ── */
    .features-section {
      padding: 3.5rem 2rem;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .feature-card {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      transition: border-color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      min-height: 180px;
    }

    .feature-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--card-border-hover);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    }

    .feature-title {
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--accent-teal);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .feature-description {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
    }

    /* ── Pricing (removed — waitlist only) ── */

    /* ── Final CTA ── */
    .final-cta {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3.5rem 2rem;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .final-cta h2 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 2.25rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .final-cta .final-subtext {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .form-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      max-width: 400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .email-input {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-family: var(--font);
      background: transparent;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
      border-radius: 4px;
      color: var(--text);
      outline: none;
      transition: box-shadow 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .email-input::placeholder {
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .email-input:focus {
      border-color: var(--accent-teal);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(94, 184, 199, 0.15);
    }

    .submit-btn {
      padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-family: var(--font);
      font-weight: 500;
      background: transparent;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
      border-radius: 4px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .submit-btn:hover:not(:disabled) {
      border-color: var(--accent-teal);
      color: var(--accent-teal);
    }

    .submit-btn:disabled {
      opacity: 0.6;
      cursor: not-allowed;
    }

    .form-message {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .form-message.error {
      color: var(--error);
    }

    .success-message {
      color: var(--accent-gold);
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .hidden {
      display: none;
    }

    /* ── Footer ── */
    footer {
      padding: 2.5rem 3rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--card-border);
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .footer-left a {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .footer-left a:hover {
      color: var(--accent-teal);
    }

    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .footer-links a {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .footer-links a:hover {
      color: var(--accent-teal);
    }

    /* ── Scroll Animation (inline in hero) ── */
    .scroll-canvas {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 520px;
      height: auto;
      aspect-ratio: 1;
      background: transparent;
    }

    /* ── Responsive ── */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .features-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }

    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      nav {
        padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      }

      .nav-link {
        display: none;
      }

      .logo-img {
        height: 50px;
      }

      .hero {
        flex-direction: column;
        padding: 7rem 1.5rem 3rem;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .hero-left {
        align-items: center;
      }

      .hero-identity {
        text-align: center;
      }

      .hero-action {
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .wordmark {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.25em;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .hero-headline {
        font-size: 1.35rem;
      }

      .hero-subheadline {
        white-space: normal;
      }

      .hero-image {
        max-width: 300px;
      }

      .btn-gold, .btn-outline {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .section-heading,
      .problem h2,
      .solution h2,
      .final-cta h2 {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
      }

      .problem, .solution, .timeline-section, .features-section, .final-cta {
        padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
      }

      .features-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .feature-card {
        min-height: auto;
      }

      .timeline::before {
        display: none;
      }

      .timeline {
        padding-left: 0;
      }

      .timeline-step {
        padding-left: 0;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        background: var(--card-bg);
        border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
        border-radius: 8px;
      }

      .timeline-step::before {
        display: none;
      }

      .form-row {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      footer {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Nav -->
  <nav>
    <a href="https://sparboesystems.com" class="logo" target="_blank">
      <img src="ss-logo.webp?v=2" alt="Sparboe Systems" class="logo-img">
    </a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#how-it-works" class="nav-link">How It Works</a>
      <a href="/guides/" class="nav-link">Guides</a>
      <a href="#waitlist" class="nav-btn">Join Waitlist</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-left">
        <div class="hero-identity">
          <h1 class="wordmark">Aurelius</h1>
          <p class="hero-headline">Your AI accountability partner. Built on Stoic philosophy.</p>
          <p class="hero-subheadline">Journal daily. Get scored nightly. Face the truth weekly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-action">
          <p class="hero-hook-setup">Most people quit journaling in two weeks.</p>
          <p class="hero-hook-punch">Aurelius makes sure you don't.</p>
          <a href="#waitlist" class="btn-gold">Join the Waitlist</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-right">
        <div class="hero-image-wrapper" id="scroll-reveal">
          <canvas class="scroll-canvas" id="scrollCanvas" width="720" height="720"></canvas>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Problem -->
    <section class="problem">
      <h2>Most people journal into the void</h2>
      <ul class="pain-points">
        <li>No one reads it back to you</li>
        <li>No one tracks whether you followed through</li>
        <li>No one tells you the pattern you can't see yourself</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="problem-closer">Aurelius does.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Solution -->
    <section class="solution">
      <h2>A discipline system, not a chatbot</h2>
      <p>Aurelius reads your journal entries, scores your day, compares your intentions against your actions, and delivers Stoic judgment. No sugarcoating. No affirmations. The truth about your week &mdash; told back to you like a mirror.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works -->
    <section class="timeline-section" id="how-it-works">
      <h2 class="section-heading">The Daily Rhythm</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">A loop designed for discipline, not engagement.</p>

      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <p class="timeline-time">Morning</p>
          <h3 class="timeline-label">Journal</h3>
          <p class="timeline-desc">Write your raw thoughts in Notion. Plans, reflections, tensions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <p class="timeline-time">9 PM</p>
          <h3 class="timeline-label">Score</h3>
          <p class="timeline-desc">Rate your day: Energy, Focus, Physical, Satisfaction. 30 seconds.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <p class="timeline-time">10 PM</p>
          <h3 class="timeline-label">Judgment</h3>
          <p class="timeline-desc">Aurelius reads everything. Names the gap between intention and action. One Stoic lens.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <p class="timeline-time">Sunday</p>
          <h3 class="timeline-label">Weekly Mirror</h3>
          <p class="timeline-desc">Full week synthesis. Patterns, wins, drift. Not a summary &mdash; a confrontation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <p class="timeline-time">Monday</p>
          <h3 class="timeline-label">Goal Check</h3>
          <p class="timeline-desc">Stale goals surfaced. Overdue commitments called out.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features -->
    <section class="features-section">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Built for Discipline</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Every feature exists to make you more accountable.</p>

      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3 class="feature-title">Stoic Judgment</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">Reads your journal. Compares stated intentions vs actions. Calls the gap.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3 class="feature-title">Daily Scoring</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">Energy, Focus, Physical, Satisfaction. Four numbers. Every night. The data of discipline.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3 class="feature-title">Weekly Narrative</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">Your week synthesized as a story. Patterns you missed. Promises you broke. Wins you earned.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3 class="feature-title">Knowledge Graph</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">Every entry makes every future entry more valuable. Compound interest on your thinking.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3 class="feature-title">Full Privacy</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">Your journal lives in YOUR Notion. We see scores, not souls.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3 class="feature-title">Bring Your Own Keys</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">Run it on your infrastructure. Your API keys. Your data. Zero lock-in.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Waitlist CTA -->
    <section class="final-cta" id="waitlist">
      <h2>The practice starts with one entry.</h2>
      <p class="final-subtext">Join the waitlist. Be first when Aurelius opens access.</p>

      <div id="formContainer">
        <form id="waitlistForm" class="form-row">
          <label for="email" class="sr-only">Email address</label>
          <input
            type="email"
            id="email"
            name="email"
            class="email-input"
            placeholder="your@email.com"
            required
            autocomplete="email"
          >
          <button type="submit" class="submit-btn" id="submitBtn">Join Waitlist</button>
        </form>
        <div id="formMessage" class="form-message hidden"></div>
      </div>

      <div id="successState" class="hidden">
        <p class="success-message">You're on the list.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
